{"tid":1650241,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Blitzchung禁賽事件繼續發酵 主播「Admirable」也宣布退出大師賽播報","createTime":"2019-10-13T01:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T05:46:08.000Z","uid":82536,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"155e5f39d940e8f97e845701d1aafae05daca272","tid":1650241,"uid":82536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:12:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-10-11/310411?f=ntk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2019-10-11%2F310411%3Ff%3Dntk&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=969c4560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-10-11/310411?f=ntk</a><br />\n<br />\nAdmirable聲明中表示，自己與暴雪合作已經5個年頭，並謹守暴雪「集思廣益」的核心價值。然而由於Blitzchung的事件，Admirable宣布退出大師系列賽剩餘播報工作，包括大師職業賽季後賽、布加勒斯特站大師巡迴賽以及世界總決賽。<br />\n<br />\nAdmirable表示Blitzchung高喊口號的行動感動了他，他決定全心支持Blitzchung。Admirable表示雖然感謝暴雪給他機會讓他能追求自己的夢想，但除非裁罰改變，不然Admirable表示自己難以相信暴雪能重新對得起「集思廣益」的核心價值，Admirable自己也無法重回主播台。Admirable表示，《爐石戰記》教會他許多事情，其中包括為了打出正確的一手，就算現在付出些許代價也在所不惜。他以此暗示暴雪，即使在短期內可能會遭遇損失，也應該做出正確的決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThatsAdmirable/status/1182429866576138240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FThatsAdmirable%2Fstatus%2F1182429866576138240&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=1d3b3e1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FThatsAdmirable%2Fstatus%2F1182429866576138240&h=efec0c76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ThatsAdmirable/status/1182429866576138240</a><br />\n<br />\n一齊去twitter 到多謝佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de5853d98afdb92ac14a5b0fbb5bbdbef0d92f7","tid":1650241,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國抵制強而有力，反觀香港人工都唔撚罷"},{"pid":"b202927c7c54ed984bca9d5352f7a9b647ac0afc","tid":1650241,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:52:32.000Z","msg":"有骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fac06493489a789dd282237b11b06020e9e0af","tid":1650241,"uid":33508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:54:29.000Z","msg":"密切關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df73129a2a2b57d6327c853e1ec89befa9451639","tid":1650241,"uid":76835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:55:00.000Z","msg":"呢d咪骨氣 港豬日日係度屌完個腐敗社會 繼續為佢服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7c65a78552a6d959f4130d5a9dc9ae07073a1f","tid":1650241,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T01:58:12.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713cb2760e4798189bccda89770401562fee144c","tid":1650241,"uid":5228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:06:20.000Z","msg":"好有型！"},{"pid":"848c24f64d74b51e552c9d9813548bb9897d6857","tid":1650241,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0ff902e74dfe43c9db196c9324f1cfa678c